    <li class="hidden-xs"><a href="https://cornell.hosts.atlas-sys.com/illiad/">Interlibrary Loan</a></li> -->
    <li><a href="http://www.library.cornell.edu/help/catalog" class="tips-link">Search Tips</a></li>
    <li class="hidden-xs"><a href="http://www.library.cornell.edu/ask">Ask a Librarian</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>
